---
import Ticket from '@components/Ticket';
import ScreenLayout from '@layouts/ScreenLayout.astro';
---

<ScreenLayout title='赞助'>
  <div class='bg-black w-full py-0 px-10 xl:px-20 overflow-hidden flex-auto flex max-w-screen-2xl'>
    <div class='flex-none justify-center h-full flex flex-col'>
      <h1 class='text-4xl leading-normal text-white'>
        DevNow Blog System <br />
        是一个开源的技术博客项目
      </h1>
      <hr class='border-dashed my-8 border-white' />

      <div class='bg-black-500 text-gray-500'>
        您的支持可以帮助更好的运营 DevNow <br />(你能找到这个页面中的二维码吗)
        <br />
        <br />找不到可以点击下面👇🏻
      </div>

      <a href='https://github.com/LaughingZhu/DevNow' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'
        ><button
          class='bg-white rounded text-center transition focus-visible:ring-2 ring-offset-2 ring-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-900 border-2 border-transparent text-black flex-none mt-8 px-1.5 py-1'
          >Sponsor me</button
        ></a
      >
    </div>
    <div class='flex-auto' id='ticket'>
      <Ticket client:only='react' />
    </div>
  </div>

  <style is:inline>
    #ticket canvas {
      width: 100% !important;
      height: 100% !important;
    }
  </style>
</ScreenLayout>
